# Liabilities Other Financial Liabilities Trade Credit Amount

## identifier
de15022

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, for trade credit purchases of goods or services for which the corresponding payment is deferred past the date on which the good or service is received.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.OtherFinancialLiabilities.TradeCredit.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo6.02.19
- period=instant
